{"tid":1683360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《外交家》討論香港「沒有國家的民族」既自治之路：「我走不下了。我會走下去。」","createTime":"2019-10-30T15:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:11:58.000Z","uid":39021,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"498b3ebe9e8f7a44d96e055cefcb4ad7cdc5bce8","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thediplomat.com/2019/10/the-future-of-hong-kongs-autonomy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2019%2F10%2Fthe-future-of-hong-kongs-autonomy%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=d4c9e7c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thediplomat.com/2019/10/the-future-of-hong-kongs-autonomy/</a><br />\n<br />\n長到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下簡單歸納<br />\n<br />\n－香港係一個「沒有國家的民族」：有政治共同體但沒有政制系統實權<br />\n－經濟上香港對中共極度重要，同時習近平上台後想大大加強中央集權，所以至習近上台後就對港實施<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「掏空政策&ldquo;take-all approach&rdquo;」：掏空一國兩制內涵，加強對香港既控制，同時用一個兩制既空殼去維持香港既經濟價值</span></strong><br />\n－流水革命係第一個成功制停「掏空政策」既運動<br />\n－中共無法接受其餘四個訴求，接受隨便一個訴求都代表要完全收回「掏空政策」，強調要集權既習近平係不能接受<br />\n－中共短期內完全技窮：既無法派解放軍，警隊信譽又完全崩潰，中共駐港傀儡網絡（中資＋中聯辦＋建制派＋黑道＋其他）亦漸漸失效<br />\n－香港政府已經無法保護西方民主國度喺香港既stake，同時中共喺全球既影響力愈黎愈大，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>西方漸漸意識到要靠自己去保護自己既stake，同時反制中共不斷強化既對外影響力</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n－<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港問題已經變成三方問題：香港人－中國－西方。因為玩家有三個，所以難以預測接落黎會發生咩事</span></strong><br />\n－未來影響中國對港政策既因素：中共政權穩定性；中共能否維持駐港傀儡網絡；中共能否喺新疆、西藏、台灣同香港同時成功維穩<br />\n－未來影響西方對港政策既因素：美國會如何控制中國擴張緊既影響力；美國會如何將香港牌放入中美地緣政治架構；美國會否進取地運用人權法；美國會否聯合西方其他國家向中國施壓<br />\n－<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港既特殊處境，令到香港既自治一定會受住其他強國（特別係中美）既影響。但作者認為香港呢個微小既「沒有國家的民族」仍然有能力改變自己命運，重點在於香港民族能否做到以下三點</strong></span>：<br />\n<strong>1. 能否進一步強化香港民族意識，抵抗中共分化戰術<br />\n2. 示威者能否將戰場擴大至全中國，以及削弱本地傀儡網絡既實力<br />\n3. 香港人能否強化全球外交網絡（即係黃之鋒同HKDA等等既角色）令西方可以更大力支持香港</strong><br />\n<br />\n－所有「沒有國家的民族」既自治之路都係不易走，隨時要以十年甚至百年做單位，香港人別無可選，只能迎難而上。作者寄語香港人應以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「我走不下了。我會走下去。」（&ldquo;I can&rsquo;t go on. I&rsquo;ll go on.&quot; by Benedict Anderson）</span></strong>呢句名言做座右銘"},{"pid":"a04fbe65f90af52b48dd289c0e7a1ce1f7385f38","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029790ed6fce32f973639bc910d3c782b23283de","tid":1683360,"uid":42119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"強化香港民族意識<br />\n完整分辨香港人同鬼國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f8c49fe5aed7436741f0c281675e1b49d7027c","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0736a80e2e07b7df3316c7de673a91f6a2fb0737","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a421191dd820f9c427f57d5470208ab5a00be59","tid":1683360,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7feb8d63e7ab17dccf5015c59c27197ee3cc4d2f","tid":1683360,"uid":65390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"一定要走下去<br />\n為不能走下去的手足走下去"},{"pid":"dca842cf610c1f358373e3929d935ff42bfe2ed5","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41547876f6c1ba927dd242768f46b4a3eb3f9da","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2157df315f6df9fed9553d179b9da0ae4a2def95","tid":1683360,"uid":42375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"1. 能否進一步強化香港民族意識，抵抗中共分化戰術<br />\n<br />\n即係要宣傳港獨意識"},{"pid":"51c8f4bf54225a5ae06c934ac3ebc7687a3012a0","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2157df315f6df9fed9553d179b9da0ae4a2def95","tid":1683360,"uid":42375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"1. 能否進一步強化香港民族意識，抵抗中共分化戰術<br />\n<br />\n即係要宣傳港獨意識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb56438af04b49930a3cbafcd2797f5c665b114","tid":1683360,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"香港民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f13494ec9e011730868f2ef2de3b5586ca2cdc","tid":1683360,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"香港立國後叫咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611d4634496d430097d7b0427858525c9faa0dc8","tid":1683360,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23faf7eb55f629d1713916f8dabda31395620462","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b651a3833dc5064a46e5a4cc9c39eb1d293417a","tid":1683360,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"cf12190c9552b3b0ff63db54fab65dc9e6066e6a","tid":1683360,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"I cant go, I'll go"},{"pid":"6e88defecb5d49e786ec50c24888d33f9538757f","tid":1683360,"uid":317939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"高質好文，要推。"},{"pid":"33bea51b05c213d638df1ee530d986bbd61f85d9","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566855cc7d1041cb2c3c9354fc30b978be99529e","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7840f5d42f98749de8fe0cbb81ea947a95511483","tid":1683360,"uid":42900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e13b5bdb895a47d5e3ae4fe48ec91276b9ef6f3","tid":1683360,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\nMotto：光復香港/榮光歸香港 + Stand With Hong Kong<br />\n國旗：待定<br />\n必修：哲學及邏輯、世界公民教育、香港民族論<br />\n軍事：入伍十八個月<br />\n經濟方針：自由主義、繼續發展relative advantage：金融、法律、IP、航運、醫學、2019年起啟蒙既軍事醫學、美容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、港式美食、旅遊、高端奢侈品貿易/拍賣<br />\n稍稍壓抑地產、點對點聯絡鄰國重點城市，毋須濫交乜三四線城市都食"},{"pid":"1726e45aeb03889257e7a8016ee932b0ee009fb4","tid":1683360,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a0da20221d3dc6a8b91617742af55b20477087","tid":1683360,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:12:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"287638386e81c26ba6afc08a75840beae17b61c6","tid":1683360,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}